<subSubSection id="C3226554361DFFA36199FA26D6E8908F" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B8736DF361DFFA36199FA26D6E8908F" blockId="4.[151,1437,1482,1687]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">
<emphasis id="B94CEACD361DFFA36199FA26D65593FB" bold="true" box="[151,267,1482,1507]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFA94B2E361DFFA36017FA26D69893FB" author="Perkins, T. H." box="[281,454,1482,1507]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" pagination="856 - 915" refId="ref14825" refString="Perkins, T. H. (1985) Chrysopetalum, Bhawania and two new genera of Chrysopetalidae (Polychaeta) from Florida. Proceedings of the Biological Society of Washington, 98, 856 - 915." type="journal article" year="1985">Perkins (1985)</bibRefCitation>
redefined the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C384D5C361DFFA363C2FA27D46393FB" authorityName="Schmarda" authorityYear="1861" box="[716,829,1483,1507]" class="Polychaeta" family="Chrysopetalidae" genus="Bhawania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B94CEACD361DFFA363C2FA27D46393FB" box="[716,829,1483,1507]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">Bhawania</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with a complete description of the body and the morphological characters of the segments, but he did not emphasize the importance of the paleae morphology. He also suggested that the species composition of 
<taxonomicName id="4C384D5C361DFFA363CEF9FFD46C9033" authorityName="Schmarda" authorityYear="1861" box="[704,818,1555,1579]" class="Polychaeta" family="Chrysopetalidae" genus="Bhawania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B94CEACD361DFFA363CEF9FFD46C9033" box="[704,818,1555,1579]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">Bhawania</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
needs to be reassesed and requires a major revision especially with regards to the paleae. This need is reflected in some species originally described as 
<taxonomicName id="4C384D5C361DFFA365F6F9DAD2379056" authorityName="Schmarda" authorityYear="1861" box="[1272,1385,1590,1614]" class="Polychaeta" family="Chrysopetalidae" genus="Bhawania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B94CEACD361DFFA365F6F9DAD2379056" box="[1272,1385,1590,1614]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">Bhawania</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but subsequently reassigned to other genera, as 
<taxonomicName id="4C384D5C361DFFA36389F9B7D346906B" authority="(Gallardo, 1968)" authorityName="Gallardo" authorityYear="1968" baseAuthorityName="Gallardo" baseAuthorityYear="1968" box="[647,1048,1626,1651]" class="Polychaeta" family="Chrysopetalidae" genus="Paleaequor" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="brevis">
<emphasis id="B94CEACD361DFFA36389F9B7D40B906B" box="[647,853,1627,1651]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">Paleaequor brevis</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFA94B2E361DFFA3626BF9B6D34E906B" author="Gallardo, V. A." box="[869,1040,1626,1651]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" pagination="35 - 279" refId="ref13562" refString="Gallardo, V. A. (1968) Polychaeta from the Bay of Nha Trang, South Vietnam. Naga report, 4 (3), 35 - 279." type="journal article" year="1968">Gallardo, 1968</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C384D5C361DFFA3655FF9B7D6EC908F" authority="(Katzmann, Laubier &amp; Ramos, 1974)" authorityName="Katzmann, Laubier &amp; Ramos" authorityYear="1974" baseAuthorityName="Katzmann, Laubier &amp; Ramos" baseAuthorityYear="1974" class="Polychaeta" family="Chrysopetalidae" genus="Arichlidon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="reyssi">
<emphasis id="B94CEACD361DFFA3655FF9B7D24E906A" box="[1105,1296,1627,1651]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">Arichlidon reyssi</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFA94B2E361DFFA3642EF9B7D6F7908F" author="Katzmann, W. &amp; Laubier, L. &amp; Ramos, J." pageId="4" pageNumber="65" pagination="313 - 317" refId="ref14197" refString="Katzmann, W., Laubier, L. &amp; Ramos, J. (1974) Une nouvelle espece Mediterraneene de Chrysopetalidae (Annelides Polychetes). Annalen des Naturhistorischen Museums in Wien, 78, 313 - 317." type="journal article" year="1974">Katzmann, Laubier &amp; Ramos, 1974</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
